
Steps : 

1. Download the Tramontana App
- iOS : https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tramontana/id1121069555
- Android : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pierdr.pierluigidallarosa.myactivity&hl=es

2. Go to js/index.js line 12 and change the ip adress for the one shown in the app.

3. Once you have applied this changes, load index.html in your browser

4. Place the screen of the device looking up

- To move up and down tilt the phone forward and backward
- Move sideways by tilting your phone from right to left or left to right
